body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, thank you for contacting Car Dealership Support. My name is Christian Young. May I please have your name?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Nicole. Could you please provide me with your phone number for verification purposes?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, it's five five five, six four three, two one eight nine.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Great, thank you. And could you confirm the spelling of your last name for me?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Nicole. Now, how can I assist you today with our Car Dealership services?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I'm feeling confused about the warranty coverage on my recent purchase.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I understand, Nicole. Let me check that information for you. Thank you for your patience.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for reaching out, Nicole. If you have any more questions, feel free to contact us anytime. Have a great day.
